}}}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
: \u8220\'3fthe taxpayer may have less freedom than the Commissioner to ignore the transactional form that he has adopted.\u8221\'3f We think this is particularly true where the yachts were transferred to the corporation in order to fulfill petitioner\rquote s specific desire to qualify them to be listed on the British Ship Registry and to fly the British flag at their sterns.
