We are not persuaded by petitioner\rquote s argument that the document which he executed purporting to be a settlement of trust, requires us to find that he held a beneficial interest in the yachts. The alleged trust is undated and appears to have only $100 in its corpus. Petitioner is not named as a beneficiary of the trust. Accordingly, we shall disregard it.
\par 
}
}
